Resource Profile: AS Donnée Publique Practitioner Profile

Official URL: https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-dp-practitioner Version: 1.0.0-ballot
Active as of 2023-06-02 Computable Name: AsDpPractitionerProfile

Profil applicatif créé à partir du profil générique as-practitioner dans le contexte des données en libre accès de l’Annuaire Santé.

Usage:

  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide

Formal Views of Profile Content

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.

  • Differential Table
  • Snapshot Table
  • Snapshot Table (Must Support)
  • All

This structure is derived from ASPractitionerProfile

Summary

Mandatory: 2 elements
Prohibited: 20 elements

Slices

This structure defines the following Slices:

  • The element Practitioner.telecom is sliced based on the value of pattern:code (Closed)
